{"tid":1533384,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"消耗戰正式開始 不被捕 不割蓆都係主要理念","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:33:08.000Z","uid":42246,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"389cb88eb1bc274c1053ac061401e6b3bdda6242","tid":1533384,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:07:15.000Z","msg":"雖然燒山係燈 但岩岩有幾單新聞+埋 佢講得幾合理<br />\n林鄭錄音流出 蝗國停左一周一行 貿易戰蝗國冇反擊侵侵<br />\n<br />\n依三樣野都係依幾日彈出來 簡單講依家話事既係中共<br />\n佢冇我地符 只可以不停用警犬拉人 打消耗戰<br />\n<br />\n唔會有垃圾解放軍 唔會有緊急法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iuz7NBFBnQ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fiuz7NBFBnQ8&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=4510ebd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iuz7NBFBnQ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不受傷 不被捕 不割蓆 攬炒就得 盡量避免換人頭<br />\n多多同侵仔講野 叫佢拎我地做棋子用來同蝗談判<br />\n<br />\n有咁耐玩咁耐 條線已經唔係十月一</span></span>"},{"pid":"62dc08593b2bd04c4ed11ccc33f8b80dd782bd69","tid":1533384,"uid":80528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"9月3日 三罷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsGOVwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsGOVwx.jpg&h=28c298c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e73cdb8b4502035908847712637ad4d7191dca6","tid":1533384,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"如果有狗死左會點 有冇人推測到"},{"pid":"d8ca39ab0fcad040a316f1295dd42a7a1358a554","tid":1533384,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgm